#: xml/smt_scripts.xml:55
msgid "When creating a software push or an update job, normally a non-persistent patch status job is added automatically. The parent ID is set to the ID of the new job. To disable this behavior, use the <option>--no-autopatchstatus</option> option."
msgstr ""

#. (itstool) path: sect2/para
#: xml/smt_scripts.xml:62
msgid "SMT is not intended to be a system to directly access the clients or to immediately report the results back. It is a long-term maintenance and monitoring system rather than a live interaction tool."
msgstr ""

