#: xml/smt_scripts.xml:67
msgid "Job Time Lag Limitation"
msgstr ""

#. (itstool) path: note/para
#: xml/smt_scripts.xml:68
msgid "The client normally processes one job at a time, reports back the result, and then asks for the next job. If you create a persistent job with a time offset of only a few seconds, it will be repeated forever and will block other jobs. Therefore, adding jobs with a time offset shorter than one minute is not supported."
